<div id="how-it-works" class="flex items-center flex-col relative bg-yellow-50 pb-24">
  <div class="relative text-center">
    <h2 class="uppercase mt-16 md:mt-24 font-bold text-5xl px-6 py-6 md:text-6xl font-headline">
      How it works
    </h2>

    <div class="invisible md:visible absolute -bottom-8 -left-16">
      <%= image_tag "arrow.svg", class: "relative w-16 h-16 -scale-x-100 rotate-45" %>
      <span class="block font-handwritten absolute top-0 -left-2 -rotate-45 text-xl">do this</span>
    </div>

    <div class="invisible md:visible absolute absolute -bottom-8 -right-16">
      <%= image_tag "arrow.svg", class: "relative w-16 h-16 -rotate-45" %>
      <span class="font-handwritten absolute top-0 -right-2 rotate-45 text-xl">or this</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid w-full md:grid-cols-2 mt-16">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center relative md:border-r-2 md:border-black">
      <div class="md:w-2/3 px-2 md:px-0 flex flex-col">
        <div class="md:w-5/6 border-2 border-black p-4 font-bold text-center md:text-left bg-[#bc95d4] shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-headline">Search for Pairing Opportunities</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="pt-4 pb-2 flex mt-6 px-4">
          <%= image_tag "search.svg", class: "block w-2/6 w-40 h-40" %>

          <p class="block w-4/6 flex items-center md:flex-none text-xl md:text-base">
            Discover pair programming requests from our vibrant community. Customize your search by technology, time availability, or desired experience level to find the perfect match.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="md:w-2/3 px-2 md:px-0 flex flex-col mt-12">
        <div class="md:w-5/6 md:self-end border-2 border-black p-4 font-bold text-center md:text-left bg-[#bc95d4] shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-headline">Express Your Interest</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="pt-4 pb-2 flex mt-6 px-4">
          <p class="block w-4/6 flex items-center md:flex-none text-xl md:text-base">
            Once you've found a pairing request that aligns with your preferences, choose your availability and reach out to the requester. Craft a compelling message to increase your chances of being accepted as a programming partner.
          </p>

          <%= image_tag "apply.svg", class: "block w-2/6 w-40 h-40" %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="md:w-2/3 px-2 md:px-0 flex flex-col mt-12 md:mt-20">
        <div class="md:w-5/6 border-2 border-black p-4 font-bold text-center md:text-left bg-[#bc95d4] shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-headline">Await Approval</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="pt-4 pb-2 flex mt-6 px-4">
          <%= image_tag "wait.svg", class: "block w-2/6 w-40 h-40" %>

          <p class="block w-4/6 flex items-center md:flex-none text-xl md:text-base">
            After expressing your interest and sending out your application, patiently await approval from the requester. During this time, feel free to prepare for the upcoming pair programming session and stay connected with our community.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <%= image_tag "arrow.svg", class: "absolute -bottom-32 right-50 w-24 h-24 -scale-x-100 invisible md:visible" %>
    </div>

    <div class="relative flex py-5 items-center my-24 mx-12 md:hidden">
      <div class="flex-grow border-t-4 border-black border-dashed"></div>
      <span class="flex-shrink mx-4 font-handwritten font-bold text-5xl">Or</span>
      <div class="flex-grow border-t-4 border-black border-dashed"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="flex flex-col relative items-center md:border-l-2 md:border-black">
      <div class="md:w-2/3 px-2 md:px-2 flex flex-col">
        <div class="md:w-5/6 md:self-end border-2 border-black p-4 font-bold text-center md:text-left bg-[#bc95d4] shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-headline">Post your pair programming request</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="pt-4 pb-2 flex mt-6 px-4">
          <p class="block w-4/6 flex items-center md:flex-none text-xl md:text-base">
            Share your coding project or learning goals by posting a pair programming request. Let us know your preferred tech, when you're free, and what you're looking for in a coding partner.
          </p>

          <%= image_tag "post.svg", class: "block w-2/6 w-40 h-40" %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="md:w-2/3 px-2 md:px-0 flex flex-col mt-12">
        <div class="md:w-5/6 border-2 border-black p-4 font-bold text-center md:text-left bg-[#bc95d4] shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-headline">Review Received Applications</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="pt-4 pb-2 flex mt-6 px-4">
          <%= image_tag "wait.svg", class: "block w-2/6 w-40 h-40" %>

          <p class="block w-4/6 flex items-center md:flex-none text-xl md:text-base">
            Your request is live, and applications are coming in. Take some time to review profiles and find the right match for your project. The perfect coding companion is just around the corner.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="md:w-2/3 px-2 md:px-0 flex flex-col mt-20">
        <div class="md:w-5/6 md:self-end border-2 border-black p-4 font-bold text-center md:text-left bg-[#bc95d4] shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)]">
          <h2 class="text-lg font-headline">Accept one of the applications</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="pt-4 pb-2 flex mt-6 px-4">
          <p class="block w-4/6 flex items-center md:flex-none text-xl md:text-base">
            Review applications and choose the one that fits your project. Confirm your coding teammate and get ready to start working together. It's as simple as that!
          </p>

          <%= image_tag "wait.svg", class: "block w-2/6 w-40 h-40" %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <%= image_tag "arrow.svg", class: "absolute -bottom-32 right-50 w-24 h-24 invisible md:visible" %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 class="mt-16 md:mt-24 text-6xl font-bold font-handwritten">Start pairin!</h2>

  <div class="w-full flex justify-center mt-12">
    <%= image_tag "pair.svg", class: "block w-80 h-80" %>
  </div>

  <div class="flex flex-col px-4 md:px-0 mt-24 md:mt-16 items-center">
    <div class="text-center md:w-1/3">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-headline font-bold uppercase">Meet our members</h1>
      <p class="mt-8 md:mt-12 mb-4 tracking-wide text-xl md:text-base">
        We're currently in the beta phase, and our community is in its early stages of growth.
        You can help us by becoming one of our inaugural members.
        Join now to be part of the foundation and help shape the future of our community!
      </p>
    </div>

    <%= link_to new_user_registration_path do %>
      <button
        role="button"
        aria-label="Click to perform an action"
        class="flex font-headline text-2xl md:text-base cursor-pointer mt-4 md:mt-0 items-center rounded-md border-2 border-black bg-[#c9dcd8] px-12 py-3 font-bold shadow-[4px_4px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] transition-all hover:translate-x-[3px] hover:translate-y-[3px] hover:shadow-none"
      >
        Join our community
      </button>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>

